      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and took the goat, which was the sin offering for the people, and slew it; where he had slain his own: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and offered it for sin, as the first: the first offering he offered for himself, which was of the same sort. ",
        "children": [
